Esthetics, function, and longevity. These three things are always driving our process and conversations. Here we had an esthetic issue with color and old restorations. We also had traumatic nerve damage to two of the front teeth. Thank you to @lajollamicroendodontics for some amazing Root canal results. She also had minimal back teeth touching properly so the forces of her bite were very uneven and causing jaw, head, and neck pain. Restoring her smile and her back teeth allowed us to Improve Esthetics, Function, and Longevity of her teeth with decreased pain and discomfort. Porcelain work by @jeffuvdl and @utahvalleydentallab

Reno air races 2023. As a kid I got to come to the races with my dad. Camping in the grass next to the airport.  I remember it being such a thrill to be around big flying machines that were so fast and badass!  Planes like #strega #rarebear #voodoo #dagored and many more.  This year was the last year of the races and jus @thelibbygroup and I got to take Olivia and Baer to witness it all.  Camping in the grass, waking up to P-51’s firing up in the morning, runs in the mountains around Donner Lake, and enjoying the show with other pilots and aviation enthusiasts.  It ended in a somber way with a crash and answering Olivia’s questions of what happened.  The reality of what we do and the risks we’re willing to take.  Thank you @renoairraces for so many memories and growing experiences.  #stoldrag -
